items.content:
Added the new clear color context-menu string to the Polish, English, and German localization files (pl.json, en.json, de.json) so the menu entry now resolves correctly in all supported languages.

You may want to: 1) launch the app with each locale to confirm the label renders as expected; 2) run your usual UI regression pass if translations are cached.
